host-llvm
=========

This is a Buildroot host-only package that symlinks the Debian build
container's preinstalled LLVM/libclc toolchain (LLVM 22 from
apt.llvm.org) into $(HOST_DIR) so that Buildroot consumers can use it
instead of building host-llvm and host-libclc from source.

Container packages required:
  llvm-22 llvm-22-dev libllvm22 libclc-22-dev

It also provides the virtual Buildroot package:
  host-libclc

License: Apache-2.0 with LLVM-exception (matching the LLVM project).

